---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Kuzupost PhotoStrips - Terms of Service">
    <div
        class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex flex-col items-center py-16 px-4 md:px-6 overflow-hidden bg-neo-yellow"
    >
        <!-- Background accents -->
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none"
            style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #111827 25%, transparent 25%, transparent 75%, #111827 75%, #111827), repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #111827 25%, #ffffff 25%, #ffffff 75%, #111827 75%, #111827); background-position: 0 0, 10px 10px; background-size: 20px 20px; opacity: 0.1;"
        >
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-4xl flex flex-col items-center">
            <h1
                class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase text-neo-white bg-neo-black inline-block px-6 py-3 border-4 border-neo-white shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#00e5ff] transform rotate-1 mb-8 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform cursor-pointer text-center"
            >
                TERMS OF SERVICE
            </h1>

            <div
                class="w-full bg-neo-white border-4 border-neo-black p-6 md:p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#111827] space-y-6 relative"
            >
                <!-- Decorative element -->
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-16 h-16 bg-neo-cyan border-4 border-neo-black transform -rotate-12"
                >
                </div>

                <div
                    class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-neo-black font-bold font-mono"
                >
                    <p
                        class="text-2xl font-black bg-neo-pink p-4 border-4 border-neo-black shadow-[-4px_4px_0_0_#111827] mb-8 transform rotate-1"
                    >
                        Aturan mainnya sederhana. Teruslah tersenyum.
                    </p>

                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl font-black uppercase border-b-4 border-neo-black pb-2 inline-block mb-4 mt-8"
                    >
                        1. Penggunaan Layanan
                    </h2>
                    <p
                        class="leading-relaxed bg-black/5 p-4 border-l-[8px] border-neo-yellow"
                    >
                        Layanan Kuzupost PhotoStrips disediakan "sebagaimana
                        adanya". Anda bebas menggunakan alat ini untuk membuat
                        foto strip pribadi maupun komersial, selama konten yang
                        dihasilkan tidak melanggar hukum, merugikan pihak lain,
                        atau mengandung unsur kebencian.
                    </p>

                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl font-black uppercase border-b-4 border-neo-black pb-2 inline-block mb-4 mt-8"
                    >
                        2. Ketersediaan Laman
                    </h2>
                    <p
                        class="leading-relaxed bg-black/5 p-4 border-l-[8px] border-neo-cyan"
                    >
                        Meskipun kami berusaha agar aplikasi ini selalu online
                        dan responsif, kami tidak menjamin 100% uptime. Aplikasi
                        ini sangat bergantung pada kapabilitas browser dan
                        perangkat keras Anda. Jika komputer Anda lambat merender
                        kanvas, mohon bersabar.
                    </p>

                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl font-black uppercase border-b-4 border-neo-black pb-2 inline-block mb-4 mt-8"
                    >
                        3. Kepemilikan Konten
                    </h2>
                    <p
                        class="leading-relaxed bg-black/5 p-4 border-l-[8px] border-neo-pink"
                    >
                        Anda memegang hak cipta penuh atas wajah dan foto yang
                        Anda hasilkan. Kami memegang hak cipta atas desain frame
                        yang kami sediakan, tetapi Anda memiliki lisensi penuh
                        untuk mendistribusikan gambar akhir (foto Anda + frame
                        kami) kemanapun Anda suka.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-12 flex justify-end">
                    <button
                        onclick="window.history.back();"
                        class="inline-block bg-neo-black text-neo-white font-black text-lg py-3 px-6 border-4 border-neo-white shadow-[4px_4px_0_0_#111827] hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0_0_#111827] hover:-translate-y-1 active:shadow-none active:translate-y-2 transition-all uppercase tracking-widest"
                    >
                        SETUJU & KEMBALI <i class="fa fa-arrow-right ml-2"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
